Package: govtrack.us
Title: GovTrack Congressional Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the GovTrack.us API. Covers bills,
    members, votes, and committees from the 93rd Congress (1973) to present.
    Includes LLM context injection via gt_context().
